Class TreeVector

  • java.lang.Object
    • mesquite.lib.Listened
      • mesquite.lib.Attachable

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Annotatable, Commandable, CompatibilityChecker, Doomable, Explainable, FileDirtier, HNode, HTMLDescribable, Identifiable, Listable, Listenable, MesquiteListener, Renamable, Selectionable, Showable, StringLister, Trees

    public class TreeVector
extends ListableVector
implements Trees, Commandable, Identifiable, CompatibilityChecker, MesquiteListener
    A tree block. Trees are added to it when trees are read from file or stored. Many methods could be built here, for instance to go through all trees and prune taxa deleted. Translation table is stored with each TreeVector.
